data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home with scenic views in all directions of the Owyhees and Bennett Mountain! Heat up next to the wood stove during this chilly winter. Take advantage of the solar panels! Bring your animals and enjoy of this amazing piece of property. Barn has potential to house 4 horses with power and water hookups! Plenty of room to park your RV or build a shop. Come and see it today!
